<|startoftext|>Dish: vinaigrette dressing for roasted and grilled seafood
Directions: mix vinegar , oil and sugar
if needed , add the sesame oil
toss till oil is well-combined and add salt and pepper
let sit over night if possible
preheat a large heavy frying shank pan on high high heat
remove meat from pan and discard fat
pour the hot oil slowly into the pan and allow all the oil to get a good coating
while pan is still hot , place the shrimp in a single layer on the shank
roast in a large hot pan without pan over heat until skin browns and shanks have turned dark green in some places and are cooked all the way through , about 10 minutes
